%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%88%E8%BD%89socket.io&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=64bd5d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">之後先轉socket.io</a><br />\n<br />\n只要了解下就知究竟發生緊咩事。睇下後面個system點design好多時候就會有足夠理解，除非你要contribute，如果唔係根本唔洗睇太多library裡面嘅code。去到真係可能有bug，又可能冇clear documentation再睇code都未遲"},{"pid":"329f978bbd41cdd31bb525196e8160e323433aa5","tid":2019834,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"咩點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪又係好似你咁睇api寫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一層隔一層咁姐，就算assembly language都係有api<br />\n<br />\n你想深究到底就要由點創一隻language同os開始學，或者由最基本processing unit學起，你先會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a54852d310e9886756d448056e1eab0fe104852","tid":2019834,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa92a838d9625ed40687024757d8ad0ca4a38b03","tid":2019834,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f29821ee4e72770ad159854319a3c66686829ba","tid":2019834,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29b1cad6a3da50f71eecd4117c654c59b330703c","tid":2019834,"uid":158499,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得點解啲library點解出極都咁難睇得明，要特登去學，完全唔user friendly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T23:58:10.000Z","msg":"識用得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"啲高手會話垃圾programmer先會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟個manager 係會認真理解人地背後個implementation先會再去用人地個api"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"咁係幾負責任嘅"},{"pid":"0be93e1072e46b58e335afca1bd02dd05fcfd0fb","tid":2019834,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18