s://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3fdcd70d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy</a>"},{"pid":"eda395acf72f0c870818a28d18882b7b778bc1d5","tid":2019834,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"其實一般嚟講唔洗明<br />\n<br />\n你係廚師，你負責煮餸，你唔洗明點樣養牛同種米<br />\n<br />\n學下無壞，不過只有少數人會走到好深，到嗰時你已經轉左職做農夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69b93b6e1177287e6b0626ccd81079a404b2f2c","tid":2019834,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e9b23087d5a42449baea47dc11463cb63fa9d0","tid":2019834,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4de773f5acec612d8500487a91e22aa5ffb5b3","tid":2019834,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"樓上個個講到咁撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係真係咁難，稍微玩過下real-time <a href=\"http://messaging都知socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmessaging%E9%83%BD%E7%9F%A5socket.io&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=e19c8e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">messaging都知socket.io</a>只係個喺websocket/long polling/short polling嘅wrapper+啲handler<br />\n<br />\n我開始玩real time messaging, <a href=\"http://socket.io/web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsocket.io%2Fweb&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=24fbdc32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">socket.io/web</a> socket未普及，所以自己寫過short polling, long polling等，再自己寫websocket，<a href=\"http://之後先轉socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%88%E8%BD%89socket.io&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=64bd5d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">之後先轉socket.io</a><br />\n<br />\n只要了解下就知究竟發生緊咩事。睇下後面個system點design好多時候就會有足夠理解，除非你要contribute，如果唔係根本唔洗睇太多library裡面嘅code。去到真係可能有bug，又可能冇clear documentation再睇code都未遲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"好似jQuery咁，今時今日socket io已經冇咩用"},{"pid":"aee2395a2dc2ab403223fb71f32f32f6fc44614e","tid":2019834,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"125e17db0e7b3cb7b452086f8a822ee05a7b5681","tid":2019834,"uid":76747,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"洗鬼理咩<br />\n所謂programmer都係user來<br />\n識google keyword &amp; 上網抄就夠啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"唔係寫kernel既都係user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d8b9012b28f81c476264ada46eec5afd7d0ef8","tid":2019834,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://github.com/cjntaylor/node-cmake\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcjntaylor%2Fnode-cmake&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=37599cb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/cjntaylor/node-cmake</a><br />\n<br />\n我見樓主淨係寫web,俾個nodejs連接low level既library writer你睇下<br />\n<br />\n其實好多library既底層都係用C/C++寫成, 再compile成library, 係一堆class/function既集合, 佢會連接到其他唔同既C/C++ library, 包括系統本身既kernel, e.g. storage, network service<br />\n<br />\n點樣連接, 點樣傳送呢D資料, 就有一定既protocol,定時有人開會去傾大家要跟咩standard, 然後就會有community去跟新既protocol修改d library, 同時有d廠都會唔跟標準去做, e.g. MS以前好興自己玩一套佢自家既standard, 近幾年唔知係咪做得open source野多d野就跟返標準做<br />\n<br />\n當你寫好呢埋C/C++ 既source後, 就會compile成library再用language本身既底層接口去引返入去用, 呢樣野叫extension, 而d language本身其實都係用C/C++寫成, 再port做一個high level language 俾你用"},{"pid":"1366cbe21ae4c116f21fc137aef2690963d45037","tid":2019834,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eda395acf72f0c870818a28d18882b7b778bc1d5","tid":2019834,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"其實一般嚟講唔洗明<br />\n<br />\n你係廚師，你負責煮餸，你唔洗明點樣養牛同種米<br />\n<br />\n學下無壞，不過只有少數人會走到好深，到嗰時你已經轉左職做農夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"但係你如果識多得啲養牛種米嘅知識<br />\n就會有助你了解唔同品種牛肉同米嘅特質<br />\n同埋知道咩季節邊度嘅食材會靚成本會平<br />\n適合用嚟配搭唔同嘅菜餚<br />\n帶出食材最優嘅煮法同食法<br />\n俾到最好嘅客人<br />\n同時你工夫又易做成本又低<br />\n<br />\n唔識嘅話就可能會一手好牌都玩到攬炒"},{"pid":"340340f4d8ecce91d5e96ec5402bb41764b5fc59","tid":2019834,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73dca7db0e056f772dbe7c90a26afcb7af7a971c","tid":2019834,"uid":13544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"196a1d02e3e7ed0a4b5d28fc36ea0b0757d0bf09","tid":2019834,"uid":43842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c06a0f1ad55c4de477a7e24e76823408f7be2e40","tid":2019834,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"公司唔會要求唔用library咩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"邊間公司咁癲唔用lib全部自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始睇唔明library既source code其實好正常<br />\n因為呢類library經歷過唔少次既performance improvement同security enhancement 變左一堆正常人好難理解到既野<br />\n<br />\n你要睇返當中business logic點解要咁行 先會諗得通人地寫乜<br />\n<br />\n以你而家個level應該係要學點樣理解同用人地寫出黎既野<br />\n將佢地提供到既野用係自己想做既事物上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"一係就有版權因素<br />\n如果唔係應該得啲痴線佬會revamp過個lib<br />\n<br />\n讀書嗰陣想你學嘢就梗係叫你自己揼一個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"唔想俾錢買版權費就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用部份open source野個licese又會要求你開返果part既source code, 其實你唔同GNU用返apache果堆library都已經ok了"},{"pid":"1aab47a3aedf9f1eed1084b0ced40528881d5345","tid":2019834,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61715e0676ff88de99217841538881e019efe571","tid":2019834,"uid":108285,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"Library係前人種樹後人食果既concept，簡單到例如一開始電得加減乘除，你想寫個function出黎計sqrt()，已經係一個function，愈來愈多function就join左個lib出黎，咁你會唔會話，公司唔比用lib，我由sqrt開始寫起呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"原生C++有math library既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過咁計, math operation library係直接去cpu 指令集, 有專門logic gate去做運算, 你到最後都一定會call到x64個library<br />\n<br />\n所以&quot;唔俾用library&quot;呢句係一個偽命題來, 只係你唔可以用邊套library要自己寫<br />\n<br />\n你唔好講你威到寫machine code自己有一套cpu指令集, 你咁威水應該入左intel/amd/nvidia既晶片公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7638b272d090add28e3c3c3abb48131520555ba3","tid":2019834,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcff91c828c74a987be54ceb2eaa0e8970488d7b","tid":2019834,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"點解啲人咁無私去main去update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實有developer會科水入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"因為堆developer自己有需要用到果個function, 上手寫套library既人又要求下手你用就一定要俾全世界睇返你改左咩<br />\n<br />\n當然係有專職團體做呢d工作, e.g. linux kernel, android, tensorflow, xnu kernel, open bsd, 全部都係大公司俾錢去develop, 當係自己既產品一部份"},{"pid":"eafe9b0d30e640072e7450261692d192cedb8729","tid":2019834,"uid":67527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dcff91c828c74a987be54ceb2eaa0e8970488d7b","tid":2019834,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"點解啲人咁無私去main去update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實有developer會科水入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"細project就通常獨立donation啦<br />\n<br />\n有啲大project就係公司open source啦，一般嚟講都唔會係公司core業務嘅code。咁open source咗之後，可以唔洗比錢有人幫你寫，其實幾抵玩。另一類就係open source之後會對你喺行業競爭上有優勢嘅，例如Google就係用kubernetes去喺cloud platform上，嘗試令到GCP有優勢<br />\n<br />\n另一啲大project就係有啲基金喺後面支持，例如Linux Foundation Apache Software Foundation之類，而依啲基金點運作？一般嚟講都係有一堆外面嘅contributors，再加一啲foundation裡面嘅maintainer，而因為佢哋嘅software/library一般嚟講都係好大，好多大公司都會用，個library maintain得好對於嗰堆公司都有著數，所以大公司都會sponsor/成為member。<br />\n<br />\n例如Apache software foundation嘅platinum sponsor就有Facebook AWS Microsoft Tencent Verizon Google等<br />\n<br />\nLinux foundation就行membership，咁要喺啲project上面有話語權就基本上要成為member，都係吸錢嘅其中一個方法"}]}